  <entry>
    <title>Linux系统下VMware kernel Module Updater弹框，Install失败</title>
    <link href="http://xinghuohan.cn/2020/10/16/Linux/VmWarekernelModuleUpdater/"/>
    <id>http://xinghuohan.cn/2020/10/16/Linux/VmWarekernelModuleUpdater/</id>
    <published>2020-10-16T08:03:05.580Z</published>
    <updated>2020-10-16T08:11:50.651Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Ubuntu系统更新后，打开VMware提示需要更新安装，点击安装失败问题解决<a id="more"></a></p><ol><li><p>提示框<img src="/media/sunfy/project/hexo-project/sunfeiyang-boke/source/img/image-20201016160643674.png" alt="image-20201016160643674" srcset="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20300%20300'%3E%3C/svg%3E" data-src="/media/sunfy/project/hexo-project/sunfeiyang-boke/source/img/image-20201016160643674.png" class="lozad post-image"></p></li><li><p>安装失败<img src="/media/sunfy/project/hexo-project/sunfeiyang-boke/source/img/image-20201016160730834.png" alt="image-20201016160730834" srcset="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20300%20300'%3E%3C/svg%3E" data-src="/media/sunfy/project/hexo-project/sunfeiyang-boke/source/img/image-20201016160730834.png" class="lozad post-image"></p><pre class="highlight"><span class="line">--处理方法</span><br><span class="line">--打开终端执行如下代码</span><br><span class="line">VMWARE_VERSION=workstation-15.5.1</span><br><span class="line">TMP_FOLDER=/tmp/patch-vmware</span><br><span class="line">rm -fdr $TMP_FOLDER</span><br><span class="line">mkdir -p $TMP_FOLDER</span><br><span class="line">cd $TMP_FOLDER</span><br><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/mkubecek/vmware-host-modules.git</span><br><span class="line">cd $TMP_FOLDER/vmware-host-modules</span><br><span class="line">git checkout $VMWARE_VERSION</span><br><span class="line">git fetch</span><br><span class="line">make</span><br><span class="line">-- 执行如下代码时需要输入管理员密码，输入完成后执行当前代码，但是后续的代码会终止，需要手动拷贝未执行其余命令继续操作，全部命令执行完成后，VMware即可正常使用</span><br><span class="line">sudo make install</span><br><span class="line">sudo rm /usr/lib/vmware/lib/libz.so.1/libz.so.1</span><br><span class="line">sudo ln -s /lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libz.so.1</span><br><span class="line">/usr/lib/vmware/lib/libz.so.1/libz.so.1</span><br><span class="line">sudo /etc/init.d/vmware restart</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Ubuntu系统更新后，打开VMware提示需要更新安装，点击安装失败问题解决</summary>
    
    
    
